		"excerpt": "We are pleased to offer VigLink as the first app in the CloudFlare Apps Dashboard. VigLink is a free app that makes it easy for you to earn revenue from your site's outbound links. ",
		"feature_image": "https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/KxhIohHvBXj8iJz8yaHNZ/27d2d7940835389c4e63745b1d69db5a/app-a-day-1-increase-your-sites-revenue-with.png",
		"featured": false,
		"html": "<p>It&#39;s officially June (in Greenwich Mean Time), so it&#39;s time for CloudFlare Apps to kick-off an <a href=\"/cloudflare-apps\">App a Day</a>.</p><p>We are pleased to offer VigLink as the first app in the CloudFlare Apps Dashboard. VigLink is a free app that makes it easy for you to earn revenue from your site&#39;s outbound links. VigLink&#39;s technology automatically turns any unaffiliated links into affiliated links where it can, which means that you earn revenue for sending visitors to other people&#39;s websites. Not only does Viglink help to earn revenue for your site, but they provide detailed analytics of where your visitors are going once they leave your site. It&#39;s pretty slick!</p>\n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/3C2X28hkXcKvcrwrus0FHn/ba6527ed0d2aab619824c475b87a2c52/viglink-200.png.scaled500.png\" alt=\"App a Day #1 - Increase your Site's Revenue with VigLink\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"200\" height=\"48\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure><p>Since VigLink is the first CloudFlare App to launch, we&#39;ve put together step-by-step instructions on how to turn it on. There are two ways to access CloudFlare Apps. The first way is that you can visit the <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/apps/\">Apps page</a>, then select the App you want. The other is to login to your CloudFlare account, where you will see a CloudFlare Apps link next to Reports &amp; Stats.</p><p>On the App Detail page, you will see a green Manage button. After selecting Manage, you will be taken directly to the CloudFlare Apps page where you can turn VigLink on.</p>\n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/50AZzvEWvsp1RAsoFa2u1J/a06a7feb06a4e3fa7902fab9d7a29428/viglink-apps-detail-top.png.scaled500.png\" alt=\"App a Day #1 - Increase your Site's Revenue with\nVigLink\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"500\" height=\"242\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure>\n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/19lC0cc0Rw4MBpH0brTZKr/2273af5ef342317a2fb520fe3d23a20d/zone-apps-page-viglink-off.png.scaled500.png\" alt=\"App a Day #1 - Increase your Site's Revenue with\nVigLink\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"500\" height=\"199\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure><p>Toggle from OFF to ON and you&#39;re done: VigLink&#39;s code is properly placed on your website.</p>\n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/7mZLwPrUkj65S8TVpkpVGl/50376e65988686a0bd7a516daeb2c2d0/zone-apps-page-viglink-on.png.scaled500.png\" alt=\"App a Day #1 - Increase your Site's Revenue with\nVigLink\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"500\" height=\"188\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure><p>If you have multiple domains on CloudFlare, then from the Apps page, you can navigate to each one of your domains to turn VigLink on. It&#39;s that simple.</p><p>CloudFlare and VigLink are excited to be partners and look forward to hearing your feedback. So, what are you waiting for? Go to the <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/apps/viglink/\">VigLink Apps page now</a>!</p>",
		"id": "7v18pJgFM8JAuHfx1lp0uF",
